, \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schuaffele is arguably the hottest player in men's golf after winning two major championships in the last three months, and enters Paris playing the best golf of his career.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 536, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967462827, \"rank\": 3.253668682057636e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's just Schauffele.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States also boasts world No.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9810911166046724, \"rank\": 0.01203483965391435, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 Scottie Scheffler, who won the Masters in April and is also playing the best golf of his young career.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 651, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scottie Scheffler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottie_Scheffler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scheffler has won six times since March, and stands with Schauffele as the two best players on the planet currently.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 870, \"en