e at the U.S. Open at Pinehurst earlier this summer.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lowry led The Open in Scotland after two rounds, and finished solo 6th.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9085627957691632, \"rank\": 0.09928490895480929, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jon Rahm and David Puig comprise the all-LIV Spain team.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jon Rahm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jon_Rahm\"}, {\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Puig\", \"score\": 0.9999435957730194, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Puig\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Puig\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Puig\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9951595766984686, \"rank\": 0.004759417065131302, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rahm played well at The Open and has been a stalwart on the LIV Tour in his first season.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Bowl_LIV\", \"score\":